Activity.description: write movie start and end time into query
Activity.body:
import groovy.text.Template import groovy.text.SimpleTemplateEngine
binding = ["tstartmovie":tstartmovie, "tendmovie":tendmovie]
engine = new SimpleTemplateEngine() template = engine.createTemplate(adqlquery).make(binding)
adqlquery = template.toString()
jes.info(adqlquery)

Activity.description: set start and end time for movie to nearest hour
Activity.body:
import java.util.Calendar import java.text.SimpleDateFormat cal = Calendar.getInstance() traceDateFormat = new SimpleDateFormat("yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss")
cal.setTime(traceDateFormat.parse(tstartmovie)) cal.set(Calendar.MINUTE,0) refstarttime = traceDateFormat.format(cal.time)
cal.setTime(traceDateFormat.parse(tendmovie)) cal.set(Calendar.MINUTE,0) cal.add(Calendar.HOUR,1) refendtime = traceDateFormat.format(cal.time)
jes.info(refstarttime) jes.info(refendtime)

Activity.description: write refstarttime and refendtime into query
Activity.body:
import groovy.text.Template import groovy.text.SimpleTemplateEngine
binding = ["refstarttime":refstarttime, "refendtime":refendtime]
engine = new SimpleTemplateEngine() template = engine.createTemplate(adqlquery).make(binding)
adqlquery = template.toString()
jes.info(adqlquery)
